Every professor at Southwest is great. Don't believe everything you read on the professor rating websites. They are not always true.

Southwest Tennessee Community College is a great school, whether taking summer classes to get ahead or seeking a career. The professors are very helpful and willing to set aside time for any student in need. With their many locations there is always one close to you.
